text: Hony Hill is a mountain in Schoharie County, New York. It is located south- southwest of Middleburgh. Armlin Hill is located south-southwest, Cotton Hill is located northeast, Cheese Hill is located south-southwest, and Windy Ridge is located east-southeast of Hony Hill. ==References== Category:Mountains of Schoharie County, New York Category:Mountains of New York (state)
title: Hony Hill
